00:00:12.250 --> 00:00:16.020
He's summited
Everest three times.

00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:18.450
The first time
discovering the body

00:00:18.450 --> 00:00:21.200
of George Mallory,
British climber who

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:23.550
