and working on it, promoting it,

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:46.240
and founded the Khumbu
Climbing Center in Nepal

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:49.200
in 2003 with his wife and
continues to do really good

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:53.000
work there promoting
responsible, safe mountain

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:53.760
climbing.

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:56.090
And today we're going to
hear him talk about Everest.

00:00:56.090 --> 00:00:57.210
So Conrad, welcome.

00:00:57.210 --> 00:00:58.698
Thank you for being here.

00:00:58.698 --> 00:00:59.694
