-The New Zealander
Edmund Hillary

00:13:58.190 --> 00:14:00.710
got his first mail and
congratulatory telegrams

00:14:00.710 --> 00:14:02.520
from George Lowe,
a fellow countryman

00:14:02.520 --> 00:14:04.400
and expedition colleague.

00:14:04.400 --> 00:14:07.760
Plus 35 miles from Kathmandu,
capital of Nepal, Hillary

00:14:07.760 --> 00:14:09.900
and Tenzing were welcomed
and congratulated

00:14:09.900 --> 00:14:11.860
by their fellow members
of the expedition,

00:14:11.860 --> 00:14:14.030
and what a bewildering
experience it must all

00:14:14.030 --> 00:14:17.520
be for the Sherpa Tenzing to be
carried from a remote mountain

00:14:17.520 --> 00:14:20.169
village and plunged into a
welter of official receptions

00:14:20.169 --> 00:14:20.710
and speeches.

00:14:30.090 --> 00:14:32.680
Tenzing brought the family along
to share in the excitement,

00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:34.920
but for all of them
the ordeal wasn't over,

00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:37.100
for now came the
inevitable questioning

00:14:37.100 --> 00:14:38.840
about that moment
of near disaster

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:41.940
when Tenzing's presence of mind
saved his friend and colleague

00:14:41.940 --> 00:14:44.739
from a fatal fall.

00:14:44.739 --> 00:14:47.030
-Tenzing and I have been
climbing together a good deal,

00:14:47.030 --> 00:14:51.010
and I think we've become
a fairly happy pair.

00:14:51.010 --> 00:14:56.319
And this was just one example
of how [INAUDIBLE] and how one

00:14:56.319 --> 00:14:57.610
is always protecting the other.

00:14:57.610 --> 00:15:00.050
I was leading down
the ice fall, and when

00:15:00.050 --> 00:15:02.420
I was crossing a crevasse
a large clump of ice

00:15:02.420 --> 00:15:04.230
gave way on which
I was standing,

00:15:04.230 --> 00:15:07.040
and I set sent off
down a crevasse.

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:09.680
Well, Tenzing here
was following,

00:15:09.680 --> 00:15:13.570
had the rope tight on a very
short time, and pulled me up

00:15:13.570 --> 00:15:15.490
so I didn't go very far.

00:15:15.490 --> 00:15:18.940
-And how did Tenzing feel up
there on top of the world?

00:15:18.940 --> 00:15:21.565
-[SPEAKING NEPALI]

00:15:21.565 --> 00:15:26.134
-[SPEAKING NEPALI]

00:15:26.134 --> 00:15:27.297
